title: My Girlfriend Is A Soap Opera Star
description:
Description :
        Janet, an actress, and Junet, a guy who works at the same company, have feelings for each other. Junet finally confesses to her, but Janet has to refuse him to accept a role in a TV series. Junet wants to wait for her, but he is forced to marry May, Janet’s new personal assistant

chapters.chapter_name: Chapter 2: Episode 2: My Time... Is Near...
